Sentencas: In order to simulate the contact situation of interconnect/contact layer/cathode in SOFC stacks, contact resistance and chemical compatibility of LaNi0.6Co0.4O3- (LNC) as contact layer between Crofer22APU interconnect and La0.6Sr0.4FeO3 (LSF) cathode was investigated at 800 degrees C in air for more than 1300h using X-ray diffraction (XRD), scanning electron microscopy (SEM) set-up equipped with an energy dispersive X-ray analyser (EDX) and area specific resistance (ASR) measurements.
Titulo: Chemical Compatibility and Electrical Contact of LaNi0.6Co0.4O3-δ (LNC) between Crofer22APU Interconnect and La0.6Sr0.4FeO3 (LSF) Cathode for IT-SOFC

Sentencas: The XRD analysis reveals that multiple phases were formed during ASR test.
Titulo: Chemical Compatibility and Electrical Contact of LaNi0.6Co0.4O3-δ (LNC) between Crofer22APU Interconnect and La0.6Sr0.4FeO3 (LSF) Cathode for IT-SOFC

Sentencas: The point microanalysis on cross-section of Fe-Cr/LNC/LSF system, after ASR measurements, shows chromium within the porous contact material mainly concentrated close to interconnect, but no Cr, Ni, or Co was detected in the cathode.
Titulo: Chemical Compatibility and Electrical Contact of LaNi0.6Co0.4O3-δ (LNC) between Crofer22APU Interconnect and La0.6Sr0.4FeO3 (LSF) Cathode for IT-SOFC

Sentencas: It was found between LNC and LSF cathode, a thin and uniform layer which contains Sr, La, Cr, Co, Ni, and Fe.
Titulo: Chemical Compatibility and Electrical Contact of LaNi0.6Co0.4O3-δ (LNC) between Crofer22APU Interconnect and La0.6Sr0.4FeO3 (LSF) Cathode for IT-SOFC

Sentencas: The contact between layers could act as a physical barrier for element migration and thus can suppress degradation of the cathode for these systems.
Titulo: Chemical Compatibility and Electrical Contact of LaNi0.6Co0.4O3-δ (LNC) between Crofer22APU Interconnect and La0.6Sr0.4FeO3 (LSF) Cathode for IT-SOFC

Sentencas: The area specific resistance slope depends on the interactions between the contact material and/or cathode and the interconnect.
Titulo: Chemical Compatibility and Electrical Contact of LaNi0.6Co0.4O3-δ (LNC) between Crofer22APU Interconnect and La0.6Sr0.4FeO3 (LSF) Cathode for IT-SOFC

Sentencas: Co-containing spinels formed during ASR test can be responsible of the resistance decrease of the system, related to the low degradation of the cell.
Titulo: Chemical Compatibility and Electrical Contact of LaNi0.6Co0.4O3-δ (LNC) between Crofer22APU Interconnect and La0.6Sr0.4FeO3 (LSF) Cathode for IT-SOFC
